      • translateToLocal

        public static String translateToLocal​(String unlocalizedName,
                                      String locale)
        Translate unlocalized entry to localized entry.
        Parameters:
        unlocalizedName - The unlocalized entry.
        locale - The language to be translated to.
        Returns:
        The localized entry. If the localized entry doesn't exist, it will first look up the fallback language map. If the entry still doesn't exist, then return the unlocalized name.
